Ngeneric:Invisible-Pin|pin@6||-42|-1|||||SIM_spice_card(D5G1;)S[* CMOS OR Gate Test (3 Separate Graphs),* Logic: Output High if A=1 OR B=1,* ------------------------------------------------,* 1. POWER SUPPLY,V_pwr vcc 0 DC 5,.global vcc gnd vdd VDD,R_tie1 vcc vdd 1m,R_tie2 vcc VDD 1m,* 2. INPUT SIGNALS (Binary Count 00 -> 11),* Input B (Fast): Period 10us,Vb B 0 PULSE(0 5 0 1n 1n 5u 10u),* Input A (Slow): Period 20us,Va A 0 PULSE(0 5 0 1n 1n 10u 20u),* 3. TRANSISTOR MODELS,.model NMOS nmos (level=1 vto=0.7 kp=20u lambda=0.02),.model PMOS pmos (level=1 vto=-0.7 kp=10u lambda=0.02),* 4. THE CIRCUIT (CMOS OR Implementation),* Structure: NOR Gate followed by Inverter,"* (If you are running this on your own schematic, you can remove this block)",* --- STAGE 1: NOR Gate (Output at 'nor_node') ---,* Pull-Up (PMOS in Series) - Only High if Both A AND B are Low,M1 node_x A vcc vcc PMOS,M2 nor_node B node_x vcc PMOS,* Pull-Down (NMOS in Parallel) - Low if A OR B is High,M3 nor_node A 0 0 NMOS,M4 nor_node B 0 0 NMOS,* --- STAGE 2: Inverter (Output at 'C') ---,* Flips NOR to OR,M5 C nor_node vcc vcc PMOS,M6 C nor_node 0   0   NMOS,* 5. SIMULATION COMMAND,.tran 10n 20u,* 6. PLOTTING COMMANDS,.control,    run,    * Window 1: Input A,"    plot v(A) title \"Graph 1: Input A (Slow)\"",    * Window 2: Input B,"    plot v(B) title \"Graph 2: Input B (Fast)\"",    * Window 3: Output C,"    plot v(C) title \"Graph 3: Output C (OR Result)\"",.endc,.end]
