Ngeneric:Invisible-Pin|pin@47||-56|-1|||||SIM_spice_card(D5G1;)S[* CMOS XNOR Gate Simulation (12 Transistors),*** Power supply,VDD Vdd 0 5,*** Input stimuli (Binary Counter for Truth Table 00-01-10-11),* A: Slow bit (40ns period),VIN1 A 0 PULSE(0 5 0n 1n 1n 20n 40n),* B: Fast bit (20ns period),VIN2 B 0 PULSE(0 5 0n 1n 1n 10n 20n),*** SECTION 1: Input Inverters (Create A_bar and B_bar),* Inverter for A -> A_bar,M1 A_bar A Vdd Vdd PMOS W=2u L=1u,M2 A_bar A 0   0   NMOS W=2u L=1u,* Inverter for B -> B_bar,M3 B_bar B Vdd Vdd PMOS W=2u L=1u,M4 B_bar B 0   0   NMOS W=2u L=1u,*** SECTION 2: XNOR Core Logic,"* Output Node = \"C\"",* --- Pull-Up Network (PMOS) ---,* Logic: (A=0 AND B=0) OR (A=1 AND B=1),* Remember: PMOS turns ON with Logic 0.,* Branch 1 (Left side): Inputs A and B,* Turns on if A=0 and B=0,M5 N_P1 A     Vdd  Vdd PMOS W=4u L=1u,M6 C    B     N_P1 Vdd PMOS W=4u L=1u,* Branch 2 (Right side): Inputs A_bar and B_bar,* Turns on if A_bar=0 (A=1) and B_bar=0 (B=1),M7 N_P2 A_bar Vdd  Vdd PMOS W=4u L=1u,M8 C    B_bar N_P2 Vdd PMOS W=4u L=1u,* --- Pull-Down Network (NMOS) ---,* Logic: (A=0 AND B=1) OR (A=1 AND B=0),* Remember: NMOS turns ON with Logic 1.,* Branch 1 (Left side): Inputs A_bar and B,* Turns on if A_bar=1 (A=0) and B=1,M9  C    A_bar N_N1 0 NMOS W=2u L=1u,M10 N_N1 B     0    0 NMOS W=2u L=1u,* Branch 2 (Right side): Inputs A and B_bar,* Turns on if A=1 and B_bar=1 (B=0),M11 C    A     N_N2 0 NMOS W=2u L=1u,M12 N_N2 B_bar 0    0 NMOS W=2u L=1u,*** Load,Cload C 0 10f,*** Models,.model NMOS NMOS (LEVEL=1 VTO=0.7 KP=120u),.model PMOS PMOS (LEVEL=1 VTO=-0.7 KP=40u),*** Simulation,.tran 0.1n 50n,.control,run,* Plot Inputs and XNOR Output,"* Expected Output C: High, Low, Low, High",plot V(A) V(B) V(C),.endc,.end]
